verbose_text: While both concentrations of MO-E (z) caused cytokinesis defects, co-injections of MO-E (z) with mRNA-E (z) restored a control phenotype with, notably, the rescue of the characteristic 4-cell symmetrical organization (XREF_FIG, rescue and rescue 1/2 panels).
evidence: cytokinesis defects, co-injections of MO-E(z) with mRNA-E(z) restored
